title: Slowdive - Complete I Saw The Sun

Slowdive - The Complete (Found) "I Saw The Sun" Sessions

This complete version of "I Saw The Sun" was made with the folowing compilations found on bittorrent sites, the russain Slowdive website, and a friend:
I Saw The Sun - Unreleased Demo #1 (The russain website)
I Saw The Sun - Unreleased Demo #2 (The russain website)
Slowdive.-.I.Saw.The.Sun.unreleased.mp3.192kbps (From piratebay.se)
Souvlaki Demos and Outtakes (From the friend)

The tracklist was organized by Ataru Barreau as an album.
